join yuna (Outlined) left
yuna: You never said it would be this massive —
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
baku: I told you, no witch has ever seen it before.  I didn't know it would be really big either.
update yuna (Outlined)
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: This isn't really big. This is —
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
baku: Oh — right, one more important thing!
baku: Yuna, do you remember the basics of sorcery?
update yuna (Outlined)
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: Baku… this is not the time —
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
baku: All sorcery can be classified into two types.
baku: Sever… the red one. Like mine.
update yuna (Outlined)
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: And Sigil… the blue one... like mine.
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
baku: Even if they can resonate in harmony…
baku: ....in their purest form, they exist to destroy each other.
update yuna (Outlined)
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: ....
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
baku: Break Sigil with Sever.
baku: Break Sever with Sigil.
baku: You understand, right?
update yuna (Outlined)
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: …I understand.
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
baku: Nice!
baku: if that’s the case, let’s start the hunt!!
update yuna (Outlined)
update baku (DarkenedOutlined)
yuna: Wait —
update yuna (DarkenedOutlined)
update baku (Outlined)
